# AutoFyn stack environment overrides.
# Generate each secret once and keep them stable:
#   openssl rand -hex 32
# AGENT_INTERNAL_SECRET authorizes dashboard‚Üîagent calls.
# SANDBOX_INTERNAL_SECRET authorizes agent‚Üîsandbox calls. They must be
# different values ‚Äî sharing them defeats the compartmentalization.
# The CLI (`autofyn start`) generates both automatically at
# ~/.autofyn/.env; this template is only for users running
# `docker compose up` directly.
# AGENT_INTERNAL_SECRET=
# SANDBOX_INTERNAL_SECRET=
